data.description: New Price Correction + Seller Concessions! This luxurious 3-bedroom condo just had a price correction! Home boasts a spacious & well-thought-out split floor plan, offering ample living space & privacy. With 3 bathrooms, including two master suites, and a 2-car garage w/direct ground-floor foyer access, it combines convenience & elegance. The property has been meticulously maintained, w/fresh paint, professionally cleaned carpets, & an array of upscale features, including quartz countertops, wood plank tile, subway tile backsplash, & upgraded stainless steel appliances. an inviting space flooded with natural light, a walk-in pantry, and an upstairs patio perfect for savoring morning coffee. The primary master suite offers a spacious walk-in shower and dual sinks, while a second master bedroom boasts its own bathroom with a walk-in shower. This condo truly combines luxury, functionality, and a prime location for comfortable living.
